name: Honi - Sunset Frame - Maui Rose Polarized Lens

features: Lens: Maui Rose® - For everyday variable conditions, from full sun to overcast. The highest contrast available - excellent for fast moving sports. Provides a subtle rose tint.
Lens Material: SuperThin Glass - Provides the absolute crispest optics available. 20% to 32% thinner and lighter than standard glass, it offers the best scratch and solvent resistance.
Shape: Classic cat eye shape that complements small round, oval or heart shaped faces.
Bridge: Saddle-style fixed bridge with embedded nose pads for added comfort
Finishing Treatment: Three colour options available in a gloss finish.
